import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.hist(data['values'], bins=20, color='blue', alpha=0.7)
    ax.axvline(data['values'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['values'].mean():.2f}")
    ax.axvline(data['values'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['values'].median():.2f}")
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of volcano eruption values?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.scatter(data['width'], data['height'])
    ax.set_xlabel('Width')
    ax.set_ylabel('Height')
    plt.title('Is there a correlation between the width and height of volcano eruptions?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 7))
    ax.boxplot(data['values'])
    ax.axhline(y=data['values'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='-', label=f"Mean: {data['values'].mean():.2f}")
    ax.legend(loc='best')
    plt.title('What is the average value of volcano eruptions?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.astype({'values': 'int32'})
    value_counts = data['values'].value_counts()
    value_counts.plot(kind='bar')
    plt.axhline(y=value_counts.max(), color='r', linestyle='-')
    plt.legend([f'Most common value: {value_counts.idxmax()}'])
    plt.title('What is the most common value for volcano eruptions?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data.sort_values(by='date')
    plt.plot(data['date'], data['values'])
    plt.title('How does the value of volcano eruptions vary over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
